header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - FINAL

videos.description: Duke gets out in transition and Tre Jones lobs it up to RJ Barrett who throws it down.
videos.headline: Jones goes up to Barrett for the slam

videos.description: Florida State gets the turnover and it ends up with Mfiondu Kabengele who throws down the thunderous two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: FSU runs fast break to perfection for dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets out in transition and flies to the rim for the big time two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Zion soars to the rim for the dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson forces the turnover and RJ Barrett leaks out and throws down the powerful one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Barrett gets the steal and flies in for the dunk

videos.description: Florida State's defense has no chance as Tre Jones finds Zion Williamson for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Jones finds Zion for the jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson and RJ Barrett combine for 23 points in the first half as Duke and Florida State are tied 36-36.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Duke knotted up with FSU at half ) 2019/03/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Duke knotted up with FSU at half

videos.description: Zion Williamson throws the perfect bounce pass to Tre Jones who puts it in with the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Zion drops dime to Jones for reverse layup

videos.description: Duke gets the turnover and gets out in transition leading to a Tre Jones lob to RJ Barrett who hammers it down with two hands.
videos.headline: Duke steal leads to Barrett slam

videos.description: Cameron Reddish puts the game away with a 3-pointer that rattles home as Duke defeats Florida State for the ACC Championship.
videos.headline: Reddish 3-pointer seals ACC Championship for Duke

videos.description: Zion Williamson is so proud of his teammates and says this is why he came to Duke: to win championships.
videos.headline: Zion: I love my brothers
